Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:34.27,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:35.49,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:37.49,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Otose...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:41.28,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this silly fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.50,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make peace and \Ncelebrate at my bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.00,Main01,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.16,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Pirako, you're coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:50.61,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Since you made a real mess of things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:54.12,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to make up for it\Nwith one hell of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.05,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Otose...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.05,Main01,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha babbling about, old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.75,Main01,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.94,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Finish up your business then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.81,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you guys going to lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.18,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,This old lady came out here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:11.31,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,despite being seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:13.96,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your petty bickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:18.32,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,There's a serious fight in the \Nworks, with Edo on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:22.92,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't protect \Nthis town, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.92,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,We may be moving in \Ndifferent directions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.83,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,but we all started in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:30.33,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,The yakuza, trannies, cabaret girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:34.09,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,We all love this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:39.08,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.85,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.91,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you wanna snuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.56,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the Four Devas while I'm around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.81,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,come back in a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.32,Main01,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.72,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you fools doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.70,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You always return the \Nfavor, seven for three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.45,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Gran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.12,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Show them our...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:09.12,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,No, show them the Kabuki \NDistrict's might.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:15.46,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,'Tis An Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.30,Main01,Teruhiko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:23.80,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,A bandit who's opened \Nthe door to paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.32,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine the lock picker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:26.81,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.81,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you shut the door \Nwithout saying anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:33.56,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how hard it \Nwas for me to get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.55,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,They found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.91,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.12,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.32,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.30,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.53,Main01,Teruhiko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.54,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You scared him because of your \Nfunny clothes, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.04,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.40,Main01,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:56.04,Main01,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,The Kabuki Cats are here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.10,Main01,Yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.09,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you fools doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.55,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna stand around while \Nthe Amanto take over our town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.06,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Katsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:13.62,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, we were the \Ncastoffs of society
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.08,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,until the boss took us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.62,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,We're prepared to throw away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:24.07,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,our worthless lives for the \Nboss, and for his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.47,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:28.60,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't gonna abandon \Nthe town our boss
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.60,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,has dedicated his life to protecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.58,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,We have a duty to protect \Nthe Kabuki District!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.83,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good, hard look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:40.09,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,This is the town your old \Nman has been protecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.34,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:46.01,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The whole universe will learn \Nto fear the Jirocho Gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:50.60,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The Kabuki District belongs to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.17,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.20,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who made \Na mess of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.11,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't stand yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:08.78,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,The Kabuki District belongs to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.40,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.79,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to us trannies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:19.34,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time for us to go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.30,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Show them the true power of a tranny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.05,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Loud and clear, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:33.22,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Kabuki District!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:34.05,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Fr-Freaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:39.16,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them in the name of the Harusame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.13,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Finish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Pops,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,we promise to protect everything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.47,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,which was dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.01,Main01,Tatsugoro,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:40.98,Main01,Tatsugoro,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of her... Take \Ncare of our town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.41,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.41,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,There were only two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:07.42,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,My elite soldiers lost \Nto these base monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.66,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be... This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:17.47,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.16,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Otose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:29.98,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected this filthy \Ntown to be home to such heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.49,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Mark my words, Jirocho...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:36.99,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,The Harusame will return this favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.70,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,All this effort to chase \Na vixen out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.63,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get any older.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:09:00.91,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,But you young'ns are disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.46,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a young lad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The elderly always let nostalgia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.27,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,cloud their memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get any older.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.44,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.78,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Is that his jutte?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.96,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:25.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I made a one-sided promise, \Nand then I swiped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.04,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.10,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.05,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I smoke, the \Nmemories come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.18,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I would watch from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.98,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,as he walked around, toying with his jutte
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.02,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,while smoking with his left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.92,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,It was rather striking to see him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.98,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Kabuki District as a backdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:53.08,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,He loved this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:56.57,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm sure that this town loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:01.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We can smoke and fiddle with a jutte,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:04.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but we can never be like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:07.74,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,He died the way he lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.63,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Like a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.45,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,who sacrificed his life \Nfor someone like me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.05,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,while leaving loved ones behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.09,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:23.47,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,So I had to give up on being \Na man, on being human,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:27.06,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,in order to protect what he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.80,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the town hated me for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So you weren't trying to kill Gran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:40.11,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:44.12,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Squawking in my ear whenever \NI did something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:48.79,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,My resolve would waver when I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.80,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,When I watched you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:55.42,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I would get the urge to go \Nback to being the old Jirocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.46,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting in my way, Tatsugoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:04.14,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:09.64,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see who's worthy of \Ninheriting his pipe and jutte.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in any inheritances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to keep \Nmy promise this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:21.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that neither of \Nus is going to cave or give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:26.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...there's only one way \Nfor us to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:35.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep my promise and survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,In return...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:39.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...you will keep your promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:45.16,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are chained to \Nthis town by the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.56,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,A promise made to a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:53.35,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,An iron vow of your own choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.12,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,The chains of a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.57,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Your promise was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:19.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.60,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.35,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you cut me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:35.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep my promise this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Pops,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,we promise to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.48,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,everything which was dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:45.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Quit smoking, old timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:13:00.25,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it if you \Nnever woke up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.67,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, you wouldn't put \Na guy in the same room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,as the person he stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.72,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.66,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Must be some kind of haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.27,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, Seirogan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:16.77,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone managed \Nto survive somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.88,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Had nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.77,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives were saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.72,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter spent
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.82,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,three days taking care \Nof you without any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.53,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,And your daughter kept an eye on me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:33.04,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure I didn't run off \Nagain and exacerbate my injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.72,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,A futile effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.09,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,We can stab you, tie you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.36,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll still get back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:42.05,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk, stubborn mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:45.49,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm stubborn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:50.91,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,but you make me look like \Na reasonable fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:56.06,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody turned out to \Nbe as twisted as he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:14:00.55,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you're worse \Nthan Tatsugoro was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.72,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,since you beat me in a battle of wills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:07.03,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty happy for \Nsomeone who was beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.07,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.46,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since \NI've had a real fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:17.08,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,A real fight between men and warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:21.09,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I can only laugh after losing \Nin such a satisfying way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:25.29,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I've given up so much to be \Nable to keep my promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:30.64,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,But he managed to save everything \Nto keep his promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.68,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:35.81,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.69,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared of losing \Nanyone else dear again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:44.69,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,He shattered the ungainly \Nchains around my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:49.70,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,They made it clear that they could \Nprotect this town without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.90,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.42,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I spend twenty years keeping my promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.35,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.29,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.90,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I just made everyone around me unhappy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.71,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,while failing to keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.22,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Otose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:11.22,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,You've done a lot for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:15.23,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,But I kept running in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:19.23,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:24.73,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.26,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.74,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What are people doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:36.20,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,It was about to get good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.58,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.34,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for bringing \Nsuch a big camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.07,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.36,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,How often are we gonna get to see \Nthe boss in a romantic scene?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.47,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Men are so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.53,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The sensitivity of a brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.92,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What's that in your hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.11,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.01,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Recording mode off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.37,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:54.54,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You were recording!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:55.60,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You were recording the entire time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.98,Main01,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing here so late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.66,Main01,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.90,Main01,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize what \Nkind of place this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:03.21,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,This is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.56,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how much \Neffort it took to get
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.61,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the old lady on top of the roof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.49,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:13.11,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You and Gintoki will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.74,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You're both selfish jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:20.61,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,The difference is that he had \Npeople to help him realize
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:26.67,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,that other people needed \Nhim the way he needed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:32.27,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you can see that \Nthere's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:35.19,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of fools \Nin the Kabuki District
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.64,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to carry on the spirit \Nof you and Tatsugoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.62,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You did a fine job of \Nprotecting this town
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:43.08,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,until the next generation \Ncould take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.12,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You kept your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.65,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,So you can let go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:55.24,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You have other promises to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:00.49,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy right now, Jirocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.21,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I met Tatsugoro here \Nin the Kabuki District.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.71,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,And I met them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:11.76,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,And I met our beloved Jirocho again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:20.79,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything, Jirocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.48,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:29.09,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,My eyesight's starting to fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.82,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,First, I can't control my bowels,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:35.24,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,now I'm leaking up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:39.24,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.24,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get any older.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.91,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow them \Nto get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.16,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Devas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.84,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.88,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,I will do anything to obtain \Nthe Kabuki District.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.88,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Lady Kada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.88,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:58.39,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you not interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:02.39,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to see my old man look...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.88,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:06.89,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand that you're \Nthe one who's interfering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.90,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.90,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,My interference is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:14.44,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm taking you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.45,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.95,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Br-Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.54,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing yourself \Nto take out the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.59,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,won't be enough to make up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.46,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,for everything you've done, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:31.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha gonna do now, Pirako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.74,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,My job is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.47,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,You can have your way with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:43.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to settle \Nthings with your old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.73,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.98,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,You took all the glory though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:52.04,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who saved my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.48,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to protect him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.94,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.15,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,This town has
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:02.43,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,wonderful people who help one another
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.04,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,despite their differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.99,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,They do more than take away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.61,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,If I could be like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.86,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.90,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,The father I wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:17.76,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,The father who Mom and I were waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:21.39,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,...is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.46,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Bro... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:28.07,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't apologize for what I've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.28,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,but let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.68,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me see my
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.52,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,father one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:40.23,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be my father's \Ndaughter or the Bro's underling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:44.48,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,but I was very happy to be \Na resident of this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.96,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,if only for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.57,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me take responsibility \Nfor what I've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not \Nsadistic enough to beat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.18,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,up a crying little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Go wait at the place listed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with you once I'm healed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You better be done crying by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.06,Main01,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try that place next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:09.85,Main01,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:13.85,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Bar Chono
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.30,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.85,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know who the strongest \Nman in the Kabuki District is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:16.53,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,You must be new in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:19.61,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,Won't last long with that attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.49,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.11,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,This town is on a whole different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.11,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.97,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,With the fall of the Deva Kada
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:28.73,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and the retirement of the Deva Jirocho,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:33.11,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,the fragile balance of power \Nis beginning to crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.87,Main01,Bar,0000,0000,0000,,The town's never been this tense before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.68,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.93,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,'Tis an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:32.66,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I was born and raised in \Nthe Kabuki District of Edo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:36.05,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,where I lived as a ruffian \Nin a town of ruffians,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:40.19,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,always surrounded by steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:44.72,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I am ashamed to admit \Nthat I have walked astray
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:47.28,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,and was guided by my brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.98,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,to embark on a journey of redemption
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:51.25,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to regain that which I have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:57.74,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I have been called boss, \Nwarrior, and many other names,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:59.75,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,but I have given them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:03.96,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I am the father of Pirako Chin,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.58,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:12.18,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude, but may I ask who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:17.99,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am the newest member \Nof the Odd Jobs family
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:20.39,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Kabuki District of Edo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:23.73,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,On a journey to find my missing father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:31.68,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I was guided here by the \Nkindness of my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:35.20,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I am the daughter of Jirocho,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.93,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Pirako Chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:45.38,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,We must have been brought \Ntogether by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.01,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:51.51,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,if I accompanied you on your journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.50,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:34.97,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode: Odd or Even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:32.36,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:33.42,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Odd
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.97,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Or even?
